---
import CornellNote from '../../components/CornellNote.astro';
---

<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>실전 연습 - 상수 극한</title>
		<!-- KaTeX (Safe CDN) -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css">
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js"></script>
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js"></script>
		<style>
			body {
				background-color: #e0e0e0;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 20px;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
			}
			.solution {
				color: #444;
				background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
				padding: 10px 15px;
				border-left: 3px solid #ccc;
				margin: 10px 0;
			}
			/* Mobile Optimization for Type Headers */
			@media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
				.type-header {
					flex-direction: row !important; /* Keep side-by-side */
					align-items: center !important;
					justify-content: space-between !important;
				}
				.type-header h4 {
					font-size: 1.1rem !important; /* Slightly smaller for mobile */
				}
				.problem-link {
					font-size: 0.8rem !important;
					padding: 3px 10px !important;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<CornellNote title="상수 극한 (x → a)" chapter="Chapter 01 Practice">
			
			<div slot="cues">
				<p style="margin: 0; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a;">🚀 해결 전략 체크리스트</p>
				<ul style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 18px; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.6; color: #444;">
					<li>직접 대입 시 분모가 { "$ 0 $" }이 되는지 확인</li>
					<li>부정형({ "$ 0/0 $" })인 경우 인수분해 또는 유리화</li>
					<li>분모와 분자의 공통인수 제거(약분)</li>
					<li>미정계수는 영인자 조건을 먼저 사용</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<section>
				<!-- Type 04 -->
				<div class="type-section" id="type04">
					<div class="type-header" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 15px;">
						<h4 style="margin: 0; color: #1a1a1a; border-bottom: 2px solid #e63946; display: inline-block; padding-bottom: 5px;">
							유형 04. 0/0 꼴 (다항식)
						</h4>
						<a href="/wiki/chapter01/types/type04/" class="problem-link">연습 ✏️</a>
					</div>
					<p>다음 극한값을 구하시오.</p>
					<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.4rem; margin: var(--base-grid) 0;">
						{ "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 1} \\frac{x^2 + 2x - 3}{x - 1} $" }
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Type 05 -->
				<div class="type-section" id="type05">
					<div class="type-header" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 15px;">
						<h4 style="margin: 0; color: #1a1a1a; border-bottom: 2px solid #e63946; display: inline-block; padding-bottom: 5px;">
							유형 05. 0/0 꼴 (무리식)
						</h4>
						<a href="/wiki/chapter01/types/type05/" class="problem-link">연습 ✏️</a>
					</div>
					<p>다음 극한값을 구하시오.</p>
					<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.4rem; margin: var(--base-grid) 0;">
						{ "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 2} \\frac{\\sqrt{x+2} - 2}{x - 2} $" }
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Type 06 -->
				<div class="type-section" id="type06">
					<div class="type-header" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 15px;">
						<h4 style="margin: 0; color: #1a1a1a; border-bottom: 2px solid #e63946; display: inline-block; padding-bottom: 5px;">
							유형 06. 미정계수 (상수)
						</h4>
						<a href="/wiki/chapter01/types/type06/" class="problem-link">연습 ✏️</a>
					</div>
					<p>다음 등식이 성립하도록 하는 상수 { "$ a, b $" }의 값을 구하시오.</p>
					<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.4rem; margin: var(--base-grid) 0;">
						{ "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 1} \\frac{x^2 + ax + b}{x - 1} = 4 $" }
					</p>
				</div>

				<a href="/wiki/chapter01/limits/" class="back-link">← 개념 공부로 돌아가기</a>
			</section>

			<div slot="summary">
				<p>상수 극한의 핵심은 **'0이 되는 원인(인수)을 찾아 제거하는 것'**입니다. 분모가 0이면 분자도 반드시 0이어야 함을 잊지 마세요!</p>
			</div>
		</CornellNote>

		<script is:inline>
			if (typeof window !== 'undefined') {
				document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
					if (typeof renderMathInElement === 'function') {
						renderMathInElement(document.body, {
							delimiters: [
								{left: '$$', right: '$$', display: true},
								{left: '$', right: '$', display: false}
							],
							throwOnError : false
						});
					}
				});
			}
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
